WEBVTT

13:03.430 --> 13:04.430 line:80%
Yan, doing this

13:04.870 --> 13:06.400 line:80%
will only dirty your hands.

13:06.790 --> 13:07.880 line:80%
How he should be punished

13:07.880 --> 13:08.890 line:80%
is for the authorities to decide.

13:08.890 --> 13:11.900 line:80%
The authorities?
If I hadn't been here today,

13:12.280 --> 13:14.550 line:80%
something bad would have happened
to Changyu.
